@node 196 Anguilla
Nature and climate: Flat and low-lying islands of coral and limestone.
   Tropical climate, moderated by northeast trade winds.
Natural resources: Salt, fish, lobster.
People: Black African.
Independence: None (dependent territory of the UK)
